<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>، عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>. وَعَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1470">حُسَيْنٍ الْمُعَلِّمِ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ، </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَا يُؤْمِنُ أَحَدُكُمْ حَتَّى يُحِبَّ لِأَخِيهِ مَا يُحِبُّ لِنَفْسِهِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>